What you need to know:

Omanyala has after all done enough to earn his rightful place in the Kenyan team for the rescheduled 2021 Olympic Games that will be held in July-August this yearThe flying Omanyala, 25, not only breached the Olympic qualifying time of 10.05 seconds but did it in sensational fashion in Lagos last TuesdayAK in their effort to hit drug cheats hard passed a resolution never to allow anybody found guilty of a doping offense to represent Kenya in competition